                                課程簡介
                            

                                 
                            

                                 
                            

                                Introduction
                            





                                本課程將以循序漸進的教授方式幫助學生瞭解國際匯兌的概念、影響匯率之因素與實務操作的技巧,俾增進對於外匯理論與實務的認識與日後工作經營技巧的提升 修完本課程後，將具備判斷影響匯率升貶值的能力，有助於對公司理財、匯兌處理、個人外匯市場投資的能力，更能瞭解央行的態度與外匯的連動關係。修完本課程後，可參加『外匯人員專業能力測驗』，有興趣者，可再鑽研「總體經濟學」與「貨幣銀行學」，以增進判斷能力。

《 課程簡介 -- English 》
                                The purpose of  this course is to develop a solid understanding of foreign exchange, the factors affecting foreign exchange, and its application to investment management.  From the class, you will learn theories and at the same time  practice them to reality. Moreover, you will have the fundamental ability to tell what factors will casue a currency depreciation or appreciation.  And this will help you to manage corporate finance and   to invest in foerign exchange more efficiency.You also can take the license of professional foreign exchange capability test.  Fore further study, you can take the "Macroeconomics "and " Money and Banking" courses to enhance your ability.











